OL,3,CAmanda Knox fails to clear her name
OL,4,Cover slander charge in Italian court
OL,6,FAmanda Knox has failed to have her
OL,7,Fname cleared of a slander charge after
OL,8,Fwrongly accusing a Congolese man of
OL,9,Fmurdering her British flatmate while
OL,10,Fthey were exchange students in Italy.
OL,12,FMs Knox was convicted of the murder of
OL,13,FMeredith Kercher before being
OL,14,Fexonerated in a case that grabbed
OL,15,Fglobal attention and headlines.
OL,17,FHowever her accusation against Patrick
OL,18,FLumumba, who owned the bar where she
OL,19,Fworked, while being questioned by
OL,20,Fpolice over Ms Kercher's death landed
OL,21,Fher back in court this year.
