OL,3,CAmanda Knox fails to clear her name
OL,4,Cover slander charge in Italian court
OL,6,FIn 2016, the European Court of Human
OL,7,FRights ruled that the interrogation
OL,8,Fviolated her rights because she was
OL,9,Fquestioned without a lawyer or
OL,10,Fofficial translator.
OL,12,FBased on that ruling, Italy's highest
OL,13,FCassation Court threw out the slander
OL,14,Fconviction in November - nine years
OL,15,Fafter the same court overturned
OL,16,Fconvictions for Ms Kercher's murder
OL,17,Fagainst Knox and her Italian ex-
OL,18,Fboyfriend, Raffaele Sollecito.
