OL,3,CAmanda Knox fails to clear her name
OL,4,Cover slander charge in Italian court
OL,6,FBecause of this, and judicial reform
OL,7,Fin Italy allowing cases that have
OL,8,Freached a definitive verdict to be
OL,9,Freopened if human rights violations
OL,10,Fare found, the court ordered a new
OL,11,Ftrial.
OL,13,FMs Knox asked eight Italian judges and
OL,14,Fjury members on Wednesday to clear her
OL,15,Fof a slander charge.
