OL,3,CAmanda Knox fails to clear her name
OL,4,Cover slander charge in Italian court
OL,6,FShe told the court she wrongly accused
OL,7,Fan innocent man of the killing under
OL,8,Fintense police pressure in overnight
OL,9,Fquestioning without the benefit of a
OL,10,Flawyer or competent translator.J"I am
OL,11,Fvery sorry that I was not strong
OL,12,Fenough to resist the pressure of
OL,13,Fpolice,'' Knox told the panel in a
OL,14,Fnine-minute prepared statement. She
OL,15,Ftold them: "I didn't know who the
OL,16,Fmurderer was. I had no way to know."
OL,18,FMs Knox showed no emotion as the
OL,19,Fjury's verdict that she was still
OL,20,Fguilty of slander was read out.
