OL,3,CAmanda Knox fails to clear her name
OL,4,Cover slander charge in Italian court
OL,6,FShe will not serve any more jail time
OL,7,Fas the four years she served before
OL,8,Fher murder acquittal counts towards
OL,9,Fthe three-year sentence for slander.
OL,11,FKnox, now a 36-year-old mother,
OL,12,Freturned to Italy for only the second
OL,13,Ftime since she was freed in October
OL,14,F2011.
