OL,3,CAmanda Knox fails to clear her name
OL,4,Cover slander charge in Italian court
OL,6,FShe remained in the United States
OL,7,Fthrough two more flip-flop verdicts
OL,8,Fbefore Italy's highest court
OL,9,Fdefinitively exonerated the pair of
OL,10,Fthe murder in March 2015, stating
OL,11,Fflatly that they had not committed the
OL,12,Fcrime.
OL,14,F"I will walk into the very same
OL,15,Fcourtroom where I was reconvicted of a
OL,16,Fcrime I didn't commit, this time to
OL,17,Fdefend myself yet again," Ms Knox
OL,18,Fwrote on social media. "I hope to
OL,19,Fclear my name once and for all of the
OL,20,Ffalse charges against me. Wish me
OL,21,Fluck."
